      "text": "History will remember this moment. 🇺🇸⚽️\n\n@POTUS , Executive Director Andrew Giuliani, @SecMullinDHS & FIFA President Gianni Infantino in the Oval Office discussing America’s vision for the 2026 FIFA World Cup.. the largest sporting event in the history of the world.\n\n78 matches.\n11 U.S. host cities.\nMillions of fans.\nOne nation celebrating its 250th birthday on the world stage.\n\nThis is bigger than soccer!\nThis is legacy, patriotism, tourism, economic growth, and a chance to showcase the strength and spirit of the United States of America 🇺🇸🏆⚽️\n\nThe Golden Age of America is here!!! 🇺🇸🇺🇸",
